title: Balance Ball Beginners Workout with Suzanne Deason [MP4]
description:
Strengthen and redefine your entire body with unique workouts designed to integrate techniques from yoga, pilates and traditional strength and flexibility training. Renowned yoga and pilates teacher Suzanne Deason combines simple and accesible pilates and yoga exercises to create an effective routine.
